title: Kellyanne Conway dresses in head-to-toe leather | Daily Mail Online
text: How the West Wing was won: Kellyanne Conway dresses in head-to-toe leather day after travel ban ruling (and drops $6k on her boots and purse alone) Kellyanne Conway dressed almost entirely in black leather on Friday President Trump's counselor wore black leather boots, black leather pants, a black leather blazer and carried a black leather handbag The handbag was a $2,910 Louis Vuitton Lockme PM bag and Conway's boots were Chanel and retail for around $3,000 Conway added some color with a lightweight berry sweater and intricate statement necklace of discs, mesh and knotted chains The selection of this ensemble came the day after Conway urged Americans to go out and buy some items from Ivanka Trump's fashion line It also came the morning after the 9th U.S. Circuit Court of Appeals ruled against President Trump's immigration order Published: 21:48 GMT, 10 February 2017 | Updated: 00:08 GMT, 11 February 2017 140 shares
